00:25:19,167 --> 00:25:21,457
And they're tooled up
to the max.

370
00:25:21,458 --> 00:25:22,458
Over.

371
00:25:22,459 --> 00:25:24,082
Copy that, Blue Tit.

372
00:25:24,083 --> 00:25:26,374
You're up, Thunder.

373
00:25:26,375 --> 00:25:27,417
Let's do this.

