434
00:32:26,792 --> 00:32:28,792
Hold your position.

435
00:32:30,833 --> 00:32:32,083
Listen up, boys.

436
00:32:34,042 --> 00:32:37,124
Jones. No, I thought

437
00:32:37,125 --> 00:32:39,332
