443
00:32:47,333 --> 00:32:49,832
Sounds like trouble
back at the ranch.

444
00:32:49,833 --> 00:32:52,332
Not feeling sorry
for him, are you, Dad?

445
00:32:52,333 --> 00:32:56,291
Sympathy and empathy
are worlds apart, Albert.

446
00:32:56,292 --> 00:32:58,791
<i>Supercedes official
police business.</i>

447
00:32:58,792 --> 00:33:00,249
Quite honestly,
you can feed them all

