00:35:28,833 --> 00:35:30,667
Got it.

507
00:35:37,792 --> 00:35:39,207
Jones here.

508
00:35:39,208 --> 00:35:41,583
About time, Petru.

509
00:35:42,792 --> 00:35:44,499
We're on.

510
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:46,332
<i>Choppy waters out of Ajaccio.</i>

511
00:35:46,333 --> 00:35:48,624
